00:49:17,926 --> 00:49:27,429
Schools that assess at least 90% of their students in all groups and subjects will not be assigned an accountability and assistance level of one to three, one, two, or three.

676
00:49:27,889 --> 00:49:36,032
Any school or district with participation rates below 90% for any group of students in any subject will be placed into level three.

677
00:49:37,172 --> 00:49:46,560
As far as high school level testing is concerned, so we're talking about the legacy MCAS test, the assessment and accountability results will be reported.

678
00:49:47,400 --> 00:50:00,951
